'''乌克兰反腐败高等法院'''（{{lang-uk|Вищий антикорупційний суд України}}）是乌克兰专门从事反腐败案件审理的法院。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.unian.info/politics/10513461-ukraine-launches-high-anti-corruption-court.html|title=Ukraine launches High Anti-Corruption Court|last=|first=|date=11 April 2019|website=www.unian.info|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220325114112/https://www.unian.info/politics/10513461-ukraine-launches-high-anti-corruption-court.html|archive-date=2022-03-25|access-date=2019-05-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://ti-ukraine.org/en/news/38-anti-corruption-court-judges-pledge-allegiance-to-people-of-ukraine/|title=38 Anti-Corruption Court Judges Pledge Allegiance to People of Ukraine|last=|first=|date=2019-04-11|website=Transparency International Ukraine|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508061022/https://ti-ukraine.org/en/news/38-anti-corruption-court-judges-pledge-allegiance-to-people-of-ukraine/|archive-date=2019-05-08|access-date=2019-05-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.rferl.org/a/ukraine-s-president-poroshenko-creates-anti-corruption-court/29875480.html|title=Ukraine's President Creates Anti-Corruption Court|last=|first=|date=11 April 2019|website=RadioFreeEurope/RadioLiberty|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508060255/https://www.rferl.org/a/ukraine-s-president-poroshenko-creates-anti-corruption-court/29875480.html|archive-date=2019-05-08|access-date=2019-05-08|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

法院位于基辅市胜利大街41号大楼。受理案值超过31000美元的腐败案件。<ref name="corruption-court-29169">[https://112.international/ukraine-top-news/the-parliament-of-ukraine-adopted-a-law-on-supreme-anti-corruption-court-29169.html Ukrainian Parliament adopts Law on Supreme Anti-Corruption Court] {{Wayback|url=https://112.international/ukraine-top-news/the-parliament-of-ukraine-adopted-a-law-on-supreme-anti-corruption-court-29169.html |date=20210613180512 }}, [[112_Ukraine|112 Ukraine]] (7 June 2018)</ref>共有35名法官员额。现有38名法官，其中27人审理一审案件，另外11人处理上诉案件。
==历史==
2017年10月下旬，为顺应欧盟与国际货币基金组织的压力，波罗申科敦促议员“立即行动起来”、完善创建反腐法庭的立法工作。2017年12月，乌克兰最高拉达起草了反腐败法院的法律。<ref name="10133912-urgent">[https://www.unian.info/m/politics/10133912-urgent-anti-corruption-efforts-in-ukraine.html "Urgent" anti-corruption efforts in Ukraine], [[UNIAN|UNIAN]] (29 May 2018)</ref>经过约2000次修订，2018年6月7日以315票支持的结果通过了该法律的最终版本。2018年6月14日筹建该法院。<ref name="IUacc511967b">[https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/511967.html Law on High Anti-Corruption Court comes into force] {{Wayback|url=https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/511967.html |date=20220316071949 }}, [[Interfax-Ukraine|Interfax-Ukraine]] (14 June 2018)</ref>2018年6月26日乌克兰总统波罗申科签署了组建反腐败高等法院的法律。<ref>[https://www.unian.info/m/politics/10165775-poroshenko-signs-law-on-establishing-high-anti-corruption-court.html Poroshenko signs law on establishing High Anti-Corruption Court], [[UNIAN|UNIAN]] (26 June 2018)</ref>国际货币基金组织将审查这是否满足它的反腐败要求，作为发放175亿美元政治改革援助资金的前提。<ref name="reuters-20180608">{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-ukraine-danylyuk/ukraines-sacked-finance-minister-says-no-will-in-cabinet-for-gas-price-hike-idUSKCN1J4288 |title=Ukraine's sacked finance minister says no will in cabinet for gas price hike |last=Williams |first=Matthias |publisher=Reuters |date=8 June 2018 |accessdate=12 August 2018 |archive-date=2020-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622191611/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-ukraine-danylyuk/ukraines-sacked-finance-minister-says-no-will-in-cabinet-for-gas-price-hike-idUSKCN1J4288 |dead-url=no }}</ref>成立最高反腐法院是国际货币基金组织、世界银行和欧盟对乌获得新贷款的一项主要要求。舆论认为，此举为乌争取进一步的国际金融援助铺垫了道路。<ref>[http://www.ccdi.gov.cn/lswh/hwgc/201806/t20180621_174143.html  “乌克兰决定成立最高反腐法院” 来源：中国纪检监察报 发布时间：2018-06-22]</ref>2018年12月，该法院决定在2019年第一季度正式组建。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ukrinform.net/rubric-polytics/2602606-pm-groysman-anticorruption-court-to-be-launched-in-first-quarter-of-2019.html|title=PM Groysman: Anti-corruption court to be launched in first quarter of 2019|last=|first=|date=17 December 2018|website=www.ukrinform.net|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808002701/https://www.ukrinform.net/rubric-polytics/2602606-pm-groysman-anticorruption-court-to-be-launched-in-first-quarter-of-2019.html|archive-date=2020-08-08|access-date=2018-12-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年4月11日举行法院成立典礼，乌克兰总统波罗申科签署了任命法院38名法官的总统令。<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.president.gov.ua/en/news/vishij-antikorupcijnij-sud-maye-stati-spravzhnoyu-oporoyu-de-54686|title=The Supreme Anticorruption Court should become a true pillar of the state in the fight against corruption - President|last=|first=|date=11 April 2019|website=president.gov.ua|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421234611/https://www.president.gov.ua/en/news/vishij-antikorupcijnij-sud-maye-stati-spravzhnoyu-oporoyu-de-54686|archive-date=2019-04-21|access-date=|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://vkksu.gov.ua/en/news/solemnities-on-the-appointment-of-judges-of-the-high-anti-corruption-court-held/|title=Solemnities on the appointment of judges of the High Anti-Corruption Court held|last=|first=|date=|website=High qualification commission of judges of Ukraine|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520144236/https://vkksu.gov.ua/en/news/solemnities-on-the-appointment-of-judges-of-the-high-anti-corruption-court-held/|archive-date=2019-05-20|access-date=2019-05-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="IUacc511967b" /><ref>[https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/512072.html Poroshenko submits bill on creating Anti-Corruption Court to High Judicial Council] {{Wayback|url=https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/512072.html |date=20210828085550 }}, [[Interfax-Ukraine|Interfax-Ukraine]] (14 June 2018)<br />{{in lang|uk}} [https://www.pravda.com.ua/news/2018/06/13/7183211/ Anticorruption court launched. The CPC claims to be "substituting" the appeal] {{Wayback|url=https://www.pravda.com.ua/news/2018/06/13/7183211/ |date=20220321072227 }}, [[Ukrayinska_Pravda|Ukrayinska Pravda]] (13 June 2018)<br />[https://www.unian.info/m/politics/10144694-ukraine-s-parliament-eventually-passes-law-on-anti-corruption-court.html Ukraine's parliament eventually passes law on anti-corruption court], [[UNIAN|UNIAN]] (7 June 2018)<br />[https://www.unian.info/m/politics/10161143-ukraine-s-rada-adopts-bill-on-establishing-high-anti-corruption-court.html Ukraine's Rada adopts bill on establishing High Anti-Corruption Court], [[UNIAN|UNIAN]] (21 June 2018)</ref>2019年5月7日由法官群体选出院长{{tsl|en|Olena Tanasevych|奥廖娜·塔纳塞维奇}}。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/585940.html|title=High Anti-Corruption Court judges fail to elect head amid repeat vote|last=|first=|date=7 May 2019|website=Interfax-Ukraine|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107225930/https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/585940.html|archive-date=2020-11-07|access-date=2019-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="585977.html|title=Judge Tanasevych">{{Cite web|url=https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/585977.html|title=Judge Tanasevych elected head of HACC by secret voting|last=|first=|date=7 May 2019|website=Interfax-Ukraine|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107233333/https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/585977.html|archive-date=2020-11-07|access-date=2019-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年9月5日正式开始运作。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/586114.html|title=HACC to begin its work on Sept 5|last=|first=|date=8 May 2019|website=Interfax-Ukraine|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210102163257/https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/586114.html|archive-date=2021-01-02|access-date=2019-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="2773908-eu-welcomes">{{Cite web|url=https://www.ukrinform.net/rubric-polytics/2773908-eu-welcomes-launch-of-ukraines-high-anticorruption-court.html|title=EU welcomes launch of Ukraine's High Anti-Corruption Court|last=|first=|date=5 September 2019|website=[[Ukrinform|Ukrinform]]|accessdate=2020-11-03|archive-date=2019-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191006123231/https://www.ukrinform.net/rubric-polytics/2773908-eu-welcomes-launch-of-ukraines-high-anticorruption-court.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
